# Assets Directory

Place your application icons here:
- icon.icns - macOS app icon (512x512 or higher, in .icns format)
- icon.png - General icon (512x512 PNG)
- tray-icon.png - System tray icon (22x22 or 44x44 PNG for retina)

You can create these using tools like:
- Image2Icon (macOS)
- IconGenerator
- Or convert from PNG using iconutil command
